# Project Conventions

> **Version:** 1.0.0 | **Category:** Cat 2 (Structure) | **TrigMem Auto-Load**
> **Triggers:** "git flow", "commit format", "file structure", "project architecture"
> **Last Updated:** 2026-03-18

---

## 🔄 Git Flow Master

### Commit Format

```
TYPE: PROJECT - vX.Y.Z

- Change 1
- Change 2
```

### Types

| Type | SemVer | Usage |
|------|--------|-------|
| RELEASE | MAJOR | Breaking changes API publique |
| UPDATE | MINOR | Nouvelles fonctionnalités |
| PATCH | PATCH | Corrections de bugs |
| WIP | MAJOR | Refactoring en cours |

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
src/
├── app/                      # Next.js App Router (routing only)
├── features/                 # Business logic
│   └── [feature]/
│       ├── components/
│       ├── hooks/
│       └── actions/
├── ui/                        # Presentational components
│   ├── atoms/
│   ├── molecules/
│   └── organisms/
└── lib/                       # Library code & configs
```

---

## 📝 File Naming

```
Components      → PascalCase.tsx           # Button.tsx
Tests           → PascalCase.test.tsx     # Button.test.tsx
Hooks           → camelCase.ts             # useAuth.ts
Utils           → camelCase.ts             # formatCurrency.ts
Config files    → kebab-case.ts            # site-config.ts
Constants       → UPPER_SNAKE_CASE.ts      # API_BASE_URL.ts
```

---

## 🎯 Import Rules

### Forward Dependencies ✅

```typescript
// Feature → UI (allowed)
import { Button } from '@/ui/atoms/button'

// Feature → Lib (allowed)
import { formatCurrency } from '@/lib/utils/format'
```

### Backward Dependencies ⚠️

```typescript
// UI → Features (avoid)
// Use props drilling / Context instead

// UI → Lib/DB (avoid)
// Use Server Components / Actions
```

---

## 📚 Documentation Convention

### README.md (< 50 lines)

```markdown
# Tech Name

One-liner percutant.

**Problem:** What it solves
**Solution:** How

## Quick Start
npm install tech-name
tech-name init
```

---

## ✅ Quality Gates

- [ ] README < 50 lines
- [ ] Quick Start ≤ 3 commands
- [ ] Commands executable
- [ ] Barrel exports in place
- [ ] Forward dependencies only

